Client

Class ClientGUI

  • java.lang.Object
    • Client.ClientGUI

  • public class ClientGUI
extends java.lang.Object
    Version:
    1

    Client Gui that bridges all interaction with the user and the rest of the application. Client gui also starts the connection to the server and hands it over to a server handler to deal with.

    Author:
    Matt Jones
